devdoc.details: Simple registry containing a mapping between underlying assets and their corresponding cToken.

addCToken(address,address).details: Adds a new cToken to the registry.

changeOwner(address).details: Lets the owner transfer ownership of the contract to a new owner.

getCToken(address).details: Gets the cToken for a given underlying asset.

listUnderlyings().details: Gets the list of supported underlyings.

removeCToken(address).details: Removes a cToken from the registry.
